de.parsemis.graph
Class HPListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>

java.lang.Object
  de.parsemis.graph.HPListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>
Type Parameters:
NodeType - the type of the node labels (will be hashed and checked with .equals(..))
EdgeType - the type of the edge labels (will be hashed and checked with .equals(..))
All Implemented Interfaces:
HPGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>, HPMutableGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>, Cloneable<HPGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.io.Serializable
public class HPListGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements HPMutableGraph<NodeType,EdgeType>

List-based implementation of the HPMutableGraph interface.

It stores the required node and edge informations in different int-arrays.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
